{\pard\sb400\sa100\f0\b\fs40 IsotopeTrack v1.0.1\par}
{\pard\sa200\f0\fs24\cf3 A comprehensive software application for analyzing single particle ICP-ToF-MS (Inductively Coupled Plasma Time-of-Flight Mass Spectrometry) data.\par}

{\pard\sb300\sa100\f0\b\fs32 Key Features\par}
{\pard\sa100\f0\fs24
\tab \bullet\tab Multi-isotope particle detection\line
\tab \bullet\tab Transport rate & ionic calibration\line
\tab \bullet\tab Support for NU Instruments folders (run.info), TOFWERK files (.h5) and CSV formats\line
\tab \bullet\tab Interactive visualization and data exploration\line
\tab \bullet\tab Batch processing capabilities\line
\tab \bullet\tab Comprehensive export options\par}

